@node Top
@top Sync Journals Bib

This manual documents @code{sync-journals-bib}, an Emacs Lisp package
that reconciles the journal field values of a master BibTeX file with
the abbreviation table used by @code{org-ref} and the official
abbreviation table on the CASSI website.

@insertcopying
@end ifnottex

